  h+=mkCard('Eficiência Carga','',(lastPPM.palletsPorEntrega?fmt(lastPPM.palletsPorEntrega,1)+' plt/viagem':'—'),'','','',lastPPM.palletsPorEntrega>=15,'purple');
  const custoPerdido=(spR.saldoPendente||0)*25;
  h+=mkCard('💰 Perda Estimada','',fR$(custoPerdido),'Pallets × R$ 25','','',custoPerdido<500,'purple');
  h+=`</div>`;
  if(ppMeses.length>=1){
    h+=`<div class="charts-row" style="margin-top:8px"><div class="chart-card"><div class="chart-title">Pallets Expedidos</div><canvas id="chPalletsMes" class="ccv"></canvas></div><div class="chart-card"><div class="chart-title">R$/Pallet</div><canvas id="chCustoPallet" class="ccv"></canvas></div></div>`;
  }
  const topCli=(sp.porCliente||[]).filter(x=>x.saldo>0);
  if(topCli.length>0){
    h+=`<div class="chart-card" style="margin-top:8px;padding:14px"><div class="chart-title" style="margin-bottom:8px">🏪 Top Clientes — Pallets Pendentes</div><table style="width:100%;font-size:11px"><thead><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:var(--t3)"><th>Cliente</th><th style="text-align:right">Ret</th><th style="text-align:right">Dev</th><th style="text-align:right">Saldo</th></tr></thead><tbody>`;
    topCli.slice(0,10).forEach(c=>{h+=`<tr style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04)"><td style="color:var(--t1)">${c.nome.length>40?c.nome.substring(0,40)+'…':c.nome}</td><td style="text-align:right">${fmt(c.retirados)}</td><td style="text-align:right">${fmt(c.devolvidos)}</td><td style="text-align:right;font-weight:600;color:${c.saldo>10?'#ef4444':'#f59e0b'}">${fmt(c.saldo)}</td></tr>`});
    h+=`</tbody></table></div>`;
  }
  return h;
}

